WEBVTT

00:01:59.031 --> 00:02:00.414
He drifted away,

00:02:00.438 --> 00:02:02.723
and today I don't know where to find him.

00:02:03.593 --> 00:02:05.072
If he watches this,

00:02:05.962 --> 00:02:07.590
I hope he'll find me.

00:02:10.639 --> 00:02:14.746
Why does medicine have
so much to offer my sister,

00:02:15.540 --> 00:02:19.750
and so much less to offer
millions of people like Robert?

00:02:20.952 --> 00:02:22.242
The need is there.

00:02:22.266 --> 00:02:25.419
The World Health Organization
estimates that brain illnesses

00:02:25.443 --> 00:02:29.558
like schizophrenia, bipolar disorder
and major depression

00:02:29.582 --> 00:02:34.553
are the world's largest cause
of lost years of life and work.